ActEconomic Recovery Act (stimulus)
SubjectOrder Fixing September 1, 2010 and January 1, 2012 as the Days on which certain Sections of that Act come into force
PrecisOrder fixing a) September 1, 2010, as the day on which sections 30 and 31, subsection 32(2) and sections 33, 34,41 and 42 of the ECONOMIC RECOVERY ACT (STIMULUS) come into force, and b) January 1, 2012 as the day on which sections 25 to 29, subsection 32(1) and sections 35 to 40 of that Act come into force, as they relate to the Canada Pension Plan.
